\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 D. Protected core, repositories, and agent authority\
\pard\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\sa80\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs21 \cf0 32.	Mechanical core protection.
\f1\b0  Which enforcement shape do you prefer?\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa60\partightenfactor0

\fs20 \cf0 [ ] Separate protected-core and generated-research repositories plus separate credentials\
[ ] One repository with OS-level read-only mounts/path permissions and protected branches\
[ ] Hybrid: separate workspaces/credentials plus signed version manifests\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa80\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Suggested default: hybrid. The agent gets write access only to generated research; protected code is mounted/readable but not writable in autonomous mode.\
