\f1\b0  How should Max authorize a core change: direct coding session, explicit maintenance-mode command, reviewed pull request, or some combination?\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa80\partightenfactor0

\fs20 \cf0 Suggested default: explicit maintenance session plus reviewed diff/tests; the resident autonomous credential never gains core write access.\
